 Jobs"}],["$","h4",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-sm font-bold leading-snug text-gray-900 transition group-hover:text-emerald-600","children":"How to Apply for Government Jobs in Kenya: Complete Guide"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400","children":["10 min read"," · ","3 January 2026"]}]]}]]}]]}]}]
